dct_title_s: Europe and the Near East : Compiled and Drawn in the Cartographic Section of The National Geographic Society for National Geographic Magazine
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights and hachures. Includes index, legend, table of distances between European ports and other important world ports via shortest navigable routes and list of countries' names translated into English. Inset map: The Middle East (1:16,000,000).
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : National Geograpic Society. Cartographic Division, 1940.
